Our great balloon arches are sure to get your guests talking and will be a great addition when decorating your venue. Why not try adding fresh flowers and foliage to your balloon arch (not included). Perfect for a wedding or any celebration

Our pink balloon arch has 70 balloons which consists of:

15 x 5" - White Balloons, 
15 x 5" - White Balloons - Pearl
6 x 18" - Foil Round Balloons - Rose Gold
10 x12" - White Balloons 
8 x 12" - White Balloons - Pearl
14 x 12" - Confetti Balloons - Rose Gold Confetti
2 x 18" - White Balloons 
4m (13 feet)  Balloon Tape

This balloon arch is easy to set up but takes some time - but not hard!  You'll want a balloon pump (sold separately in the shop) and allot about 1 - 1.5 hours to blow up balloons and assemble.  The balloon tape (which is a flexible plastic strip with holes down the length) is what allows the arch to have its form (no wireframe.)  You pull the balloon knots thru the holes and build your arch.  The tape can be cut and multiple smaller arrangements can be made.  You'll be surprised how easy it is!

title: Gender Reveal Cannon, Gold Boy or Girl, Pink or Blue, He or She What Will Baby Be
description:
Reveal the baby's gender with these gender reveal confetti poppers - a unique idea! Gold poppers that you can't see thru - so you can surprise everyone with the answers to "Heels or Wheels" "Tutus or Touchdowns" "Bows or Baseball"! Mail a set to relatives long distance to announce a pregnancy or gender reveal! (See details below about how we can coordinate your reveal to surprise yourself or others!) 

Filled with tissue paper confetti in pink or blue -  these little push-pop poppers will surprise your guest with the baby's gender.  Twist the base of the popper to shoot confetti into the air.  Cannons have a removable sticker on the outside showing if boy or girl. (Please put in the notes section at checkout if you want that removed before I ship!!)

Each pack contains 1 confetti cannon measuring 11 inches (H) by 2 inches (W).


Price is for ONE popper.  Please select the total number you need!

TO ORDER:

1) Select "Boy/blue" or "Girl/Pink" from the drop-down.

2) Select the quantity that you want.

3) Add to cart

4) If you want both boy and girl poppers - see info below on how they are shipped.  Repeat the above steps to add the additional poppers to your cart.  Enter any details in the 'notes' box at checkout!

How the poppers are marked if you are ordering BOTH BOY and GIRL poppers:  If you order both types, then I will mark all of one kind with an "A" and all of the other with a "B".  A sealed envelope will be provided in the box that reveals if A or B is a boy or girl.  This way, you can give your results to someone else, and they can tell you which to open. 

Also, you can order these awaiting your appointment to send to friends and family and tell them which one to pop (and I tell YOU which is which.)  This works well if you want to order several sets, and you want to have everyone pop at once - you just tell everyone to pop "A" or number "B".  There are lots of ways to work out the details and I'd love to help make the reveal extra special!

YES! You can have someone contact me if you want the gender to be a surprise to YOU!  Just place your order, and in the NOTES TO SELLER BOX, please let me know the date that you need to receive them by, and the NAME/email of the person that will contact me with the gender.  It's a fun way to find out for everyone! 

Supervise children when using.  Point away from the face.
